HIV: China ta yi magana game da karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar HIV da kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta sanar da cewa adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke dauke da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an ma'aikatar lafiya.
An samu sabbin kamuwa da cutar kusan 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018.
Yawancin su ana yada su ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da yadda aka saba a baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar jini.
Amma a wannan hanyar, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya kusan zuwa sifili, in ji jami'an ma'aikatar lafiya ta kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau a China yana ƙaruwa da dubu ɗari a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna wariya ga LGBT na ci gaba.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda ra'ayoyin gargajiya na kasar, kashi 70-90% na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da maza, za su yi aure da mace.
Ana samun cututtuka ta hanyar yin jima'i da rashin amfani da kariya.
Bayan 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar kanjamau ga kowa domin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatanta sun fitar da bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican, tana mai kiranta "karya mai hatsari" da kuma "ka'idojin karya".
'Yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin da aka yi a ranar Asabar cewa wani ma'aikaciyarta ta raba bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku 'yan Republican kuma ta sanya su a shafin Wikipedia.
Ya yi ikirarin cewa masana da shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan adawa ne suka gudanar da tuhumar.
