An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin mata a cikin gida, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun sashen 'yan sanda na Wasilla, wanda ya ba da rahoton cin zarafin cikin gida da kuma daukar makami a lokacin da ba a farka ba.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia Sun Goyi Bayan Sabuwar Dokar Ba da Gudummawa ga 'Yan Gudun Hijira
Jihohi goma sha uku da kuma Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan kalubalen shari'a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka da ta ce ba za a ba da mafaka ga wadanda ake zargi da aikata laifi ba ko kuma wadanda ake zargi da aikata laifin a cikin gida.
A ranar Juma'a a Washington, wakilai daga jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar Columbia sun gabatar da takardar shawarwari mai kyau don tallafawa masu neman mafaka game da abin da siyasa ke kira, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a shari'ar Grace Sessions da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta kan dokar tarayya ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta "da 'ya'yanta da ke cikin wata ƙungiya mai ta'addanci" sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An kama shi a Texas.
Jami'an gwamnati da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana cewa El Salvador da Honduras da Guatemala suna da yawan neman mafaka a Amurka saboda wadannan kasashe suna fuskantar matsalar 'yan bindiga da kuma cin zarafin cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar mafaka ta Amurka ta soke shawarar da Hukumar Daukaka Kara ta Baƙi ta yanke a shekarar 2014 da ta bai wa baƙi damar tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida da kuma neman mafaka.
A wata sanarwa da ya fitar a ranar Juma'a, Janar mai kula da shari'ar gundumar Columbia Carl Racine ya ce sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yi amfani da takamaiman hujjoji da yanayin neman mafaka a kan duk wani bukatar mafaka, kuma wannan takunkumi ya sabawa wannan ka'ida", in ji mai shari'a.
Masu imani sun yi jayayya cewa dokar hana baƙi shiga ta sabawa manufofin Amurka, suna cewa za su sa su zama masu kasuwanci kuma "za su ba mu aikin da muke bukata".
Janar Trustee Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice a watan Yuni da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke fama da cin zarafin gida da na 'yan bindiga.
"Ana samun mafaka ga duk wanda ya bar kasarsa saboda tsoratarwa ko tsoron nuna bambanci saboda tserensa, addininsa, kasawarsa, ko takamaiman rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayin siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar siyasa ta ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa samun mafaka ba don magance dukan matsaloli - ko da manyan matsaloli - da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya.
Masu aikin agaji sun ba da kansu a wajen ceto a garin Palouse, inda adadin mutanen da suka mutu a cikin tseren neman masu ceto ya ninka na mutanen da suka mutu a lokacin tseren.
Yanayin ya daɗa muni ga waɗanda suka tsira.
"Ina jin na damu sosai", in ji Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiyar 'ya'ya 35, yayin da take ta'azantar da ɗanta da ke fama da zazzabi a cibiyar 'yan gudun hijira a garin Palouse da ke cike da bala'i.
"A kowane minti, motar asibiti tana kawo gawawwaki.
Ruwa mai tsafta bai isa ba".
Mutanen sun koma gidajensu da suka lalace, sun yi ta haƙa dukiyar da ke cikin ruwa, sun yi ƙoƙarin ceton duk abin da suka samu.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni, kuma asibitocin da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta shafa sun cika.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dewey Harris, wanda ke da rauni a kashin baya da kafada, suna hutawa a waje da asibitin soji na Paulo, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda ci gaba da mummunan girgizar kasa.
Hawaye suka zubo masa idanunsa ya sake fara jin dadin yadda girgizar kasa ta girgiza dakin da yake a hawa na biyar na otal din da yake zaune da matarsa da 'yarsa.
"Ba lokacin da za mu yi tserewa ba.
Na bi ta cikin bangon, ina tsammanin", in ji Harris ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press, ya kara da cewa danginsa sun je bikin aure a garin.
"Na ji mijina yana roƙon Shela, sai na yi shiru.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita da ɗana ba.
Ina fata suna lafiya".
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da 'ta'addanci' ta hanyar 'tallan farfaganda'
Mako guda bayan jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu inda Amurka ke neman a yi wa kasar Sin karin tallafi a harkar kasuwanci, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya rubuta wani labari mai tsada a ranar Laraba a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, wanda ya bayyana abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, ya zama wani sabon mataki na kara tsanantawa a yakin neman zaben da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Duk da cewa al'ada ce gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace domin inganta kasuwanci, a halin yanzu Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin cinikayya, inda suke kara haraji kan kayayyakin da juna ke shigowa da su.
An tsara takunkumin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don a yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki hari a jihohi kamar Iowa, wanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Branstead, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka wallafa a ranar Litinin a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, Bransted ya rubuta cewa, "China ta ninka wannan tashin hankali ta hanyar yada farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"A cikin yaɗa ta'addanci, gwamnatin Sin tana amfani da al'adar 'yancin magana da 'yancin latsa na Amurka ta hanyar saka tallace-tallace masu tsada a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstead.
"A gefe guda, a nan a birnin Beijing, a kan titin jaridar, za ku ga ra'ayi mai zurfi, kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayi da mutanen Sin za su iya yi ba game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China, wanda ya nuna mana cewa kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin".
Ya kara da cewa "daya daga cikin manyan jaridu na kasar Sin ya ki buga labarinsa", amma bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
Rashin Kavanaugh zai sa 'yan Republican su daina yin zabe ga mata a lokacin da ake zaɓe, manazarta sun yi gargadin hakan.
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican ke jiran kare dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh kan wasu zarge-zargen cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su yi rashin nasara a zaben fidda gwani, musamman daga mata.
Tashin hankali ya yi yawa, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun yi rajista kuma suna nuna cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Ba za a iya yin watsi da ra'ayin ba", in ji Grant Rieher, Farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Rieher ya ce yana da shakku cewa bukatar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi a minti na karshe na gudanar da bincike kan hukumar tarayya zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta ba gobe ko Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara ga ƙungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn kuma babban mai magana da yawun ƙasa a ranar Juma'a, a cewar Jaridar Washington.
A ranar Juma'a da safe a wani zanga-zanga a zauren majalisar dattawa, masu zanga-zanga sun yi ta rera "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da nuna rashin amincewar Dr. Christine Blaise Ford, in ji Mic.
"Democrat zai kasance mai matukar farin ciki da kuma himma", in ji Steve Rosenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa wanda ba ya jam'iyyar Democrat.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi girma; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin unguwannin da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ba sa yawan shiga zaben ko da yake ba sa son shugaban kasa".
Kafin Ford ya bayyana a fili cewa ya yi wa wani dan takarar babban kotun tarayya fyade, manazarta sun ce hakan zai yi illa idan 'yan Republican suka gabatar da hujjoji.
"Wannan ya zama rikici na wauta ga 'yan Republican", in ji Michael Still, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cikin rahoton NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun batun kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma na karshe, ko za a sanya Kano a kan kujera, amma kuma batun yadda 'yan Republican za su bi da wannan da kuma yadda za su bi da shi", in ji Gay Cecil, darektan fifiko na Amurka, wani rukuni da ke taimakawa zaɓen Democrat, yana mai nuni ga tashar labarai.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun nuna cewa sun fi sanin wanda za su yarda da shi a cikin shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, kuma sun fi son na biyun.
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi daga YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun gaskata da abin da Ford ya faɗa, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun gaskata da abin da Kavanaugh ya faɗa.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce Kavanaugh ya yi kuskure ko kuma ya yi kuskure a lokacin da ya ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka yi kuskure a lokacin da ya ba da shaida.
Bayan matsin lamba daga Flake, FBI tana binciken tuhumar da Ford yayi, kamar yadda akalla mai shigar da kara daya, Deborah Ramirez, ta yi, in ji jaridar Guardian.
Ford ya shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa fyade a lokacin da yake shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce wani dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aura a lokacin da suke bikin ne a lokacin da take jami'a a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo yana shirin kirkirar sabuwar yanar gizo domin ya doke Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya fara wani sabon shiri wanda zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da aka yi wa wannan ƙwararren masanin fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke gina dandalin buɗe ido na Berners-Lee, Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma abin da mutane ke da damar shiga kowane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi a lokacin da aka fara.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar samun nasu "Kayan ajiyar bayanan kan layi", ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Wannan kamar yadda Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suke a cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke banbanta da bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne, yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar irin bayanan da yake da su.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin, manufar Inrupt ita ce a ba da gudummawa ga albarkatu, aiyuka da ƙwarewa don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu ma'aikatan ci gaba da aka ba da kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma haɗin gwiwar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da "Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da wani canji na gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya zama cikakke a rana daya.
"Ba ma neman izininsu".
A cikin wata kasida da aka wallafa a kan matsakaici a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "ya kamata ya samar da wutar lantarki da kuma tsarin halittu don kare inganci da ingancin sabon cibiyar sadarwa a kan Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Har ma a lokacin da Inrupt ya fara, Berners-Lee zai zama wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan zamani na gaba na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Wani limami yana tunawa da karbar gicciyen Victoria a Yaƙin Duniya na ɗaya
An yi bikin bikin bikin karbar lambar Victoria Cross daga wani limamin Cocin Ingila a matsayin mai yaki a yakin duniya na farko, shekaru 100 bayan haka a garinsu.
Lt. Col. Clerk Bernard Van ya lashe kyautar ne a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin da ake kai hari a Bellanglis da Lecoeur.
Sai dai wani dan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana hudu, kuma bai taba sanin cewa ya samu babbar lambar yabo ta soja a Birtaniya ba.
A ranar Asabar, a lokacin bikin, jikokinsa biyu sun kafa wani abin tunawa a Rashden a Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Van, ya ce "abin da ya fi burgewa" shi ne cewa an kafa dutsen ne daidai shekara 100 bayan da kakansa ya lashe kyautar.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a cewar jaridar London Gazette, Laftanar Kanar Vann ya ja-goranci rukuninsa a kan hanyar St. Centin "a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai ƙarfi daga bindigogi da makamai masu linzami".
Sai ya kai su ga layin wuta, kuma da "ƙarfi" ya kai layin gaba zuwa ga bindigogi, ya kashe uku daga cikinsu.
Wani dan kunar bakin waken Jamus ne ya kashe Laftanar Kanar Van a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918 - daidai wata daya kafin yakin ya kare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi shi ne "abin da ba zan iya yi ba, amma abin da ya nuna tawali'u".
Shi da dan uwansa, Dr. James Wan, an kuma naɗa su a matsayin sarakuna bayan bikin da ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood ta yi.
Michael Wan ya ce "yana jin cewa ya cancanci shiga cikin wannan bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "za a iya ganin jarumin na gaskiya ta hanyar goyon bayan da mutane da yawa ke bayarwa".
Masu sha'awar wasan Mixed Martial Arts sun yi dare suna kallon Bellator 206, maimakon haka suka zaɓi Peppa the Goat.
Ka yi tunanin kana da hasken rana mai yawa don ka yi wa Bellator 206 aiki, kuma ba za ka iya zuwa babban taron ba.
San Jose ya ba da rahoto game da fadace-fadace 13, ciki har da manyan katunan shida, kuma an nuna shi kai tsaye a tashar tashoshi 5 a Burtaniya.
Da karfe shida na safe, bayan Gerard Moussa da Rory McDonald sun shirya don saduwa, masu sauraro a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka sauya watsa shirye-shiryen zuwa bututun ƙwai.
Wasu sun yi farin ciki, bayan sun yi dare suna yin wa'azi musamman don wannan daren.
Wani mai son fim ɗin ya bayyana shi a shafinsa na Twitter a matsayin "wani irin mugun wasa".
"Wannan doka ce ta jihar cewa wannan shirin na karfe shida na safe bai dace ba, don haka dole ne su canza zuwa shirin yara", in ji David Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da shirin.
"Yarinya da aka yi wa yankan zumunci".
Shugaban Bellator, Scott Coker ya bayyana cewa suna aiki kan jadawalin su don yin la'akari da masu sauraro na Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina tsammanin idan na yi tunani game da maimaitawa, zan iya tunanin wani abu", in ji Coker.
"Amma sa'a shida na safe ne a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za mu iya yin aiki a kan wannan ba har sai ranar Lahadi ce a lokacinmu, kuma ranar Litinin ce a lokacinsu.
Amma muna aiki a kan wannan.
Ku yi imani da ni, lokacin da aka canza, akwai matani da yawa da ke tafiya gaba da baya babu wanda ya kasance abokantaka.
Mun yi kokarin gyara wannan, mun yi tunanin cewa matsalar fasaha ce.
Amma ba haka ba ne. Wannan aikin gwamnati ne.
Na yi alkawari ba zan sake yin hakan ba.
Za mu yi wasanni biyar maimakon shida kamar yadda muka saba, kuma mun yi ƙoƙari mu nuna wa magoya baya cewa mun fi su, kuma mun yi kasala.
Wannan abin takaici ne".
Desert Island Discs: Tom Dale ya ji cewa yana da matukar damuwa game da sha'awar jima'i
Tom Dale, ɗan wasan motsa jiki na Olympics ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa an yi masa ba'a saboda yadda yake son yin jima'i amma hakan ya sa ya so ya yi nasara.
Ta ce ba ta fahimci hakan ba har sai da ta shiga makarantar sakandare inda "ba kowa kamar ni".
A lokacin da yake magana a tashar rediyo ta Radio 4 mai suna Desert Island Discs, wanda Lauren Laverne ke gabatar da shi, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi don "ba da bege ga wasu".
Ta kuma bayyana cewa tun da ta zama uwa, ba ta da sha'awar lashe gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin mai tsawo Kirsty Young ta yi watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
A cikin shirin farko na LaVerne, Dailey ta bayyana cewa lokacin da take girma, tana jin "kasa" saboda "ba a yarda da ita ba yayin da yara maza da mata suka so ta".
Ta ce, "Yau, wannan jin da nake yi cewa ni kasa ce kuma banbanta ba, gaskiya ne, wanda ya ba ni ƙarfi, ya sa na yi nasara".
Yana son ya tabbatar da cewa shi "wani abu ne", in ji shi, don kada ya bata wa kowa rai idan suka gano shi da jima'i.
Gwarzon dan wasan Olympics sau biyu ya zama sanannen mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don samun ƙarin ƙasashe masu halarta don yin zanga-zangar nuna bambancin jinsi.
Ta ce ta yi muryarta ne domin ta yi sa'a, ta yi rayuwa a sarari ba tare da ta yi ba, kuma tana son ta ba wa wasu "bege".
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce ya ƙaunaci wani mutum - mai shirya fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Blake, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013 - "ya kama ni ba zato ba tsammani".
Dale ya auri Oskarosan, wanda ya girme shi da shekara 20 a shekarar da ta gabata, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da na yi nasara a shekarunka", - ya fara gasar Olympics sa'ad da yake shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji bayan shekara uku - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunsa da ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali da rashin sa'a.
Sun haifi ɗa a watan Yuni, wanda suka kira Robert Ray Black-Dale, kuma Dale ya ce "darajarsa ta canza".
Ya ce, "Idan na tambaye ku a bara, abin da nake so shi ne na ci zinare".
"Ka san, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
