"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, 'Ba za ka iya zama a kan gaba ba, Baba,'" in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma hakan bai faru ba, har sai da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu, ban fahimci cewa ba shi da rai na har abada ba", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Dailey ta yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ta ci tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shine abin da nake fata a rayuwata, yin iyo a gasar Olympics a gaban magoya bayana, babu wata jin da ya fi wannan", in ji ta.
Wannan kuma ya ba da shawarar zaɓin waƙar farko ta - Proud by Heather Small - wanda ya yi wahayi zuwa gare shi yayin gasar Olympics kuma har yanzu yana da tsalle-tsalle.
Za a yi shirin Desert Island Discs a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15.
Michelson da aka yi wa kwaskwarima ya shiga gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar.
