An sake jinkirta karbar sabon jirgin ruwan yaki na Jamus
An shirya a karbi sabon jirgin ruwan sojan ruwa na Jamus a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a samu ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar kudin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
An dage karbar jirgin Rhinland-Pfalz, wanda ke dauke da sabon jirgin Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta nakalto wani jami'in soji.
An shirya jirgin ya shiga cikin jirgin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan isar da kayayyaki sun hana kammala wannan aikin mai matukar buri.
Jirgin ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg, wanda rundunar ta ba da umarni a 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
Tabbas, za su sami manyan jiragen ruwa, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da kuma wasu fasahohin da ba a san su ba, kamar su rage radar, infrared da kuma fasahar sauti.
Sauran mahimman abubuwan sune tsawon lokacin ajiya - ya kamata a iya sanya sabbin jirage daga tashar jirgin ruwa na tsawon shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, jinkiri na yau da kullum yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na zamani - waɗanda aka tsara don ƙarfafa sojojin Jamus - za su kasance marasa amfani lokacin da suka shiga aiki, Die Zeit ta lura.
Frigate F125 na Abbey ya zama sanannen labarai a shekarar da ta gabata lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwan Jamus ta ƙi karɓar jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa masana'antar Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin Jamus ta mayar da jirgin bayan da mai ginin jirgin ya kira shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka janye ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun nuna wasu manyan "ƙwarewar software da kayan aiki" wanda zai iya sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka ƙaddamar da aikinsa.
Kuskuren software ya kasance mai mahimmanci saboda jirgin Baden-Wuerttemberg yana da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120 - kawai rabin rabin tsohuwar jirgin ruwan Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa, wanda ke rage tasirinsa kuma yana iyakance ikon rundunar don ƙara haɓaka a nan gaba.
Jirgin Rhinland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 zai ninka nauyin jirgi iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Tare da matsalar kayan aiki, farashin yana hana cikakken aikin - haɗawar horo na ma'aikata - wani batun ne.
