Dundee Stars sun gyara rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Premier ta ranar Juma'a, inda suka ci gaba da buga wasan neman nasara a ranar Asabar, Dundee ta ci 5-3 a wasan da suka yi.
Giants sun ci gaba da ci biyu da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beuiller.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cooney sun kai su matakin masu masaukin baki, kafin Dwyer ya sake kafa Jagorancin Giants.
François Bouchard ya daidaita da Dundee kafin Lucas Lundwald Nielsen ya ci biyu ya sa suka ci nasara.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da aka doke Adam Kief a gasar zakarun Turai, wanda ya zo daga nesa domin kallon Dundee ta doke Belfast da ci 2-1.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da 'yan wasan suka yi karawa a kakar wasa, yayin da Giants suka ci wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya ci kwallo a karo na hudu, 3:35 ta hanyar da Kendall McFaul, da kuma David Rutherford, wanda ya ninka bambanci bayan minti hudu.
Bayan minti na farko, Sullivan ya jefa kwallo daya ga masu masaukin baki a minti 13:10 na wasan, kafin Meth Marquardt ya taimaka wa Coyne ya daidaita lissafin a minti 15:16.
Kafin a yi hutu, Dwyer ya sake sa Giants su yi barci sa'ad da ya ci kwallo na biyu a ƙarshen wasan farko.
Masu masaukin sun sake komawa, kuma Bouchard ya sake dawo da wasan da babbar nasara a minti na 27:37.
Haɗin Coyne da Charles Corcoran ya taimaka wa Nielsen ya sami damar haɓaka Dundee a ƙarshen rabin wasa na farko a cikin wasan kuma ya jagoranci tawagarsa zuwa nasara, ta biyar a ƙarshen matakin.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasan ne a gida a ranar Juma'a a Milton Keynes.
