Labarai game da Red Circuit: Rage taro a Pinellas, Menati da Sarasota
Wani rahoto da hukumar kifi da namun daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa, yawan mutanen da ke da jan jini a yankin Tampa Bay yana raguwa.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji, an yi wa garin Pinellas, Menat, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier takunkumin hana tabo - wanda ke nuna cewa an hana su taro.
An gano cewa akwai wasu wurare da ke da ruwan sama mai zafi sosai a yankin.
An samu tabo a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun garin Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa ba kamar makon da ya gabata ba.
An kuma ga jan motsi a garin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaicin kamuwa a cikin garin Pinellas ko kewayensa, daga low zuwa high a garin Hillsborough, daga low zuwa high a garin Menat, daga low zuwa high a garin Sarasota ko kewayensa, daga low zuwa medium a garin Charlotte, daga low zuwa high a garin Lille ko kewayensa, da kuma low a garin Metropolitan.
Rahotanni na ci gaba da nuna cewa akwai ciwon numfashi a cikin garuruwan Pinellas, Menate, Sarasota, Lees, da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata babu wani rahoton cutar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
